                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">You can select the account linked
                from which the funds are to be transfered to the third party.
                This account is linked to the selected entity. </para><tip>
                    <para role="TEXT">Click the Search Account <inlinemediaobject>
                        <imageobject>
                          <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_glass.gif"/>
                        </imageobject>
                      </inlinemediaobject> icon and a popup with the list of
                    available accounts appears. If required, enter values for
                    account number, or currency, or description, or a desired
                    combination of any, and click on the Search button to
                    refine the list. Click on the required account number from
                    the list to select it and it appears in the Transfer From
