                Id</guilabel> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT"> <inlinemediaobject>
                    <imageobject>
                      <imagedata fileref="../images/char_excla.gif"
                                 role="CHAR_EXCLA" width="2mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject> </para></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The name for the template, if you
                would like to create a template based on the third party
                transfer details on the screen. </para><note>
                    <para role="TEXT">Once you are finished entering details, you can
