                                 role="CHAR_INFO" width="4mm"/>
                    </imageobject>
                  </inlinemediaobject></entry>

                <entry valign="top"><para role="TEXT">The date for the third party
                transfer transaction creation. By default, this is the current
                business date and is a read-only field.</para></entry>
              </row>
